Primary Objectives
• To implement a digital pharmacy billing and inventory system that reduces manual workload
• To enable accurate, real-time tracking of medicines using batch, expiry, and GST data
• To automate stock inward, adjustments, audits, and low-stock triggers
• To deliver a fully controlled environment for store owners and admins
• To reduce operational losses due to expired medicines, stock mismatch, or unbilled sales
• To ensure compliance with pharmaceutical regulations
